{"tid":1987884,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有聽過人間先至係地獄","createTime":"2020-04-24T19:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T13:28:26.000Z","uid":200405,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"05236e6f27be11048822f76bcb597246fd5056d7","tid":1987884,"uid":200405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T19:32:48.000Z","msg":"唔知有無分宗教<br />\n但細細個已經聽過話其實在世先係地獄<br />\n你就係要刻服人世間既種種考驗<br />\n<br />\n雖然我都知依個世界依然有好多美好既人同事<br />\n但有時受過傷 好似個人點都無辦法再開心返咁<br />\n只係更加小心翼翼咁生活 怕信錯人之類 <br />\n又或者就算繼續都係帶住遺憾咁向前行<br />\n<br />\n諗起細細個好小既事都可以令到自己由心底笑出黎<br />\n當然依家既生活都好多值得感恩既事<br />\n但已經知道無辦法返返去以前"},{"pid":"db45eb6fd9697c4cabfd740747da4ecc69d35176","tid":1987884,"uid":115586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T19:33:39.000Z","msg":"他人即地獄"},{"pid":"509093c1ba751173980e2702011c58edd7edc2d4","tid":1987884,"uid":27824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T19:35:26.000Z","msg":"來回地獄又折返人間"},{"pid":"427beaf9df9eac3b3e66dd785623f3214195bac0","tid":1987884,"uid":207929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T19:35:41.000Z","msg":"細個以為係天堂 大個就知係地獄"},{"pid":"7013f5bc7d1266c77bf2fb38db5c526cf26dbda3","tid":1987884,"uid":200405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"509093c1ba751173980e2702011c58edd7edc2d4","tid":1987884,"uid":27824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T19:35:26.000Z","msg":"來回地獄又折返人間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T19:36:44.000Z","msg":"真係好攰<br />\n有時咩都唔想要 咩都唔好有期望"},{"pid":"ac0be2dcfd066956e557f6f5b3f445c46699267a","tid":1987884,"uid":200405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"427beaf9df9eac3b3e66dd785623f3214195bac0","tid":1987884,"uid":207929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T19:35:41.000Z","msg":"細個以為係天堂 大個就知係地獄"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T19:37:50.000Z","msg":"點先可以將自己既世界變返做天堂<br />\n變返當初純真既人？"},{"pid":"aa13c81ee0ecd5fc9897c691c1dfece94e1cd17d","tid":1987884,"u